{"id":4,"parent_id":0,"book_id":44,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":4,"title":"Lesson 3: “I Had Seen a Vision”","subtitle":"","short_title":"Lesson 3","uri":"/manual/doctrine-and-covenants-and-church-history-class-member-study-guide/lesson-3-i-had-seen-a-vision","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/doctrine-and-covenants-and-church-history-class-member-study-guide/lesson-3-i-had-seen-a-vision.head1"},[".titleNumber","Lesson",["span.dominant","3"]],["h1","“I Had Seen a Vision”"],[".kicker","Reading assignment:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.1-26"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:1–26"],";",["span.emphasis","Our Heritage,"],["a.crossRef",{"href":"/manual/our-heritage-a-brief-history-of-the-church-of-jesus-christ-of-latter-day-saints/chapter-one-the-first-vision.p1"},"pages 1–4."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/doctrine-and-covenants-and-church-history-class-member-study-guide/lesson-3-i-had-seen-a-vision.p4"},"After Jesus Christ was crucified, His Apostles presided over the Church. But soon persecution, divisions, and apostasy increased. Within a few decades, there was a falling away from the Church, as the Apostles had prophesied (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/20.28-30"},"Acts 20:28–30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/2.1-3"},"2 Thessalonians 2:1–3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-tim/4.3-4"},"2 Timothy 4:3–4"],"). This falling away is known as the Great Apostasy."],["ul.bullet",["li",["span.label","•"],[".para","What were some of the consequences of the Great Apostasy? (See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.15-16"},"D&C 1:15–16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.8-9,19,21"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:8–9, 19, 21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/1.13-14"},"Mormon 1:13–14"],".)"]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para","Why was Joseph confused about which church he should join? (See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.5-10"},"Joseph Smith—History 1:5–10"],".) How was Joseph’s situation like that of people today who are searching to know the truth?"]],["li",["span.label","•"],[".para","What are some of the truths we can learn from the First Vision?"]]],[".topic",["h2","Scripture Chain: The Apostasy and the Restoration"],["ul.noMarker",["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/8.11-12"},"Amos 8:11–12"]]],["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/3.20-21"},"Acts 3:20–21"]]],["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.14-17"},"D&C 1:14–17"]]],["li",[".para",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.20-21"},"D&C 128:20–21"]]]]]]],"refs":null}
